{
  "stem": "7337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the first thing was-- that's why my father wanted us to be in a boarding school, so that we would learn the language quickly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, he couldn't cope with my mother, who was very ill, and our education at the same time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we lived at school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At the same school?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was a primary school, and a-- my brother was four years younger than I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he found it very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, in fact, refused to-- to-- he said, he doesn't know why we left Germany, and he wants to go back home where people can understand him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He suffered very badly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had been through more hardships.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that for me, it was a relief to be out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we went to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I wrote-- this was 1933 that we arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wrote my matric 1934, '35.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In France, you write two matrics-- one, the first matric is the school-leaving matric.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the second one is one year later, if you go to university, you've got to write a second exam.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had no intention of going to university.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I left with the first baccalaureate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's then that I found out that I could not get a work permit as an alien, because I would have to serve three years in the French army.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And my father said, no ways can you serve in the French army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We have no valid passports.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We left Germany, and it's quite obvious that there's going to be a war between Germany and France, sooner or later.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] we didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
